plyTime":"2019-03-27T02:23:05.000Z","msg":"留名等睇自由黨同田二少投反對票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有商界 <br />\n另外美領事館又出聲屌777<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb68c1c79ca1ced0791fd3ee11e3186fef9bc115","tid":1079250,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"要拉鳩你大把理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f97f326328399fbaa8dd2bc91a6e7465675be4d","tid":1079250,"uid":65604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:35:27.000Z","msg":"你話依單野唔係任務來真係搵鬼信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}